        <p>This portfolio traces a journey — from India to Dublin — across every role and challenge that shaped how I think and how I execute.</p>
        <p>With a cross-functional background spanning payroll operations, digital marketing analytics, and strategic consultancy, I bring rigour to complexity and clarity to ambiguity.</p>
